Package org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.helperClasses.bezierCurves

Class AbstractBijectiveMap<T,S>

java.lang.Object
org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.helperClasses.bezierCurves.AbstractBijectiveMap<T,S>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of keys in the map
S - the type of values in the map
All Implemented Interfaces:
BijectiveMap<T,S>
public class AbstractBijectiveMap<T,S> extends Object implements BijectiveMap<T,S>
This is an abstract implementation of a bijective map, which allows for a one-to-one mapping between keys and values. It provides methods to put, get, invert, check existence, remove entries, and retrieve the forward and reverse maps.
